e"/></inline-formula>、<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/8-2620187x113_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>、<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/8-2620187x114_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>、<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/8-2620187x115_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>、<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/8-2620187x116_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>分别在网络节点<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/8-2620187x117_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>处做Taylor展开，由上一部分分析可知：</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.15937-formula1111"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/8-2620187x118_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><disp-formula id="hanspub.15937-formula1112"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/8-2620187x119_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>所以此格式关于<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/8-2620187x120_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>二阶相容，关于<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/8-2620187x121_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>二阶相容，其截断误差为<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/8-2620187x122_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p></sec><sec id="s7_3"><title>5.3. 数值计算结果</title><p>对(9)在<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/8-2620187x123_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/8-2620187x124_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>上做数值实验，取时间步长为<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/8-2620187x125_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，空间步长